evaluation.response:
It's great to hear that you're taking steps to break free from the cycle of constant tracking and calculation.&#x20;

It's very common to experience lingering thoughts and habits, even after making positive changes. They can be hard to shake, especially when those thoughts have become deeply ingrained over time.&#x20;



It is okay to take your time and work through these thoughts at your own pace. By acknowledging your progress and continuing to take small steps in a positive direction, you can move closer to a healthier and more balanced relationship with food and your body.
